::Battera::

She looked at him, still nervouse. "Ah, I have been waiting to see 
the leader of the Maximals. I am to invite the leader to our embassy 
on neutral ground.  The Predacon leaders will be there and so will 
the Maximal leaders." She paused and looked down. "My friends are 
contacting the other leaders." She folded her wings around her 
body,like a close fitting cloak, to cover her shaking body. She was 
still feeling the adrinalline rush from the attack. 

(I know bots don't have adrinaline, but it still has the same effect.)
